name: Seasonal Flu Shot Information
short_desc: Provides information about where to get seasonal flu shots in Alameda County
description: For Seasonal Flu Shot vaccine clinic locations contact Public Health Clearinghouse at 888-604-4636 (INFO), or visit website at www.acphd.org.For information about seasonal flu shots, go to www.acphd.org/seasonalflu and enter zip code in the Flu Vaccine Locator to learn where to get vaccinated. Vaccine supplies may be limited. Check availability; call ahead.
